### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/merge-pdf/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Merge two PDFs (needs ./samples/document.pdf — add two copies or a second PDF as part-b.pdf)
POST {{baseUrl}}/merge-pdf/merge
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MergeBoundary

--MergeBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="part-a.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./samples/document.pdf
--MergeBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="part-b.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./samples/document.pdf
--MergeBoundary--
